# VER-014: Textured Cube Golden Image Test (INDEXED8_2X2)
# 
# 12-triangle cube with per-face colour, depth testing,
# INDEXED8_2X2 white/black checker texture (encoded in the
# four quadrants of palette entry 0).
# Phase 'zclear':    initialise Z-buffer to 0x0000 (reverse-Z far)
# Phase 'palette':   stage palette + index array, trigger PALETTE0
# Phase 'setup':     configure texture and render mode
# Phase 'triangles': submit cube triangles (MVP-transformed)

## FRAMEBUFFER: 512 512

## PHASE: zclear

# Clear color buffer: base_word=0x000000 value=0x0000 count=262144
44 0400_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_FILL: base_word=0x000000 value=0x0000 count=262144

40 0000_0099_0800_0000  # FB_CONFIG: color_base=0x0000 z_base=0x0800 w_log2=9 h_log2=9
43 0000_0080_2000_0000  # FB_CONTROL: scissor x=0 y=0 w=512 h=512

## PHASE: palette

# Upload PALETTE0 blob (4096 B, 1 populated entries) at byte 0x110000.
44 0008_0000_0008_8000  # MEM_FILL: base_word=0x088000 value=0x0000 count=2048
70 0000_0000_0002_2000  # MEM_ADDR: dword_addr=0x22000
71 FF00_0000_FFFF_FFFF  # MEM_DATA: palette dword[0]
71 FFFF_FFFF_FF00_0000  # MEM_DATA: palette dword[1]
12 0000_0000_0001_0880  # PALETTE0: BASE_ADDR=0x0880 LOAD_TRIGGER=1

# Upload all-zero index blocks (4×16 B) (64 B) at word 0xC0000.
70 0000_0000_0003_0000  # MEM_ADDR: dword_addr=0x30000
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[0]
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[1]
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[2]
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[3]
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[4]
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[5]
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[6]
71 0000_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_DATA: index dword[7]


## PHASE: setup

